<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>비밀번호 찾기</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,typography"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#6366F1",
            "background-light": "#F9FAFB",
            "background-dark": "#111827",
            "card-light": "#FFFFFF",
            "card-dark": "#1F2937",
            "text-light": "#1F2937",
            "text-dark": "#F9FAFB",
            "subtext-light": "#6B7280",
            "subtext-dark": "#9CA3AF",
            "border-light": "#E5E7EB",
            "border-dark": "#374151"
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ["Noto Sans KR", "sans-serif"],
          },
          borderRadius: {
            DEFAULT: "0.5rem",
          },
        },
      },
    };
  </script>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display">
<div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
<header class="w-full px-4 py-4 md:px-8">
<div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
<a class="text-xl font-bold text-primary flex items-center" href="#">
<span class="material-icons mr-2">article</span>
          뉴스 추천
        </a>
<nav class="flex items-center space-x-2">
<a class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-subtext-light dark:text-subtext-dark hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">로그인</a>
<a class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-primary rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors" href="#">회원가입</a>
</nav>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="w-full max-w-md space-y-8 bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-md">
<div>
<h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">
            비밀번호 찾기
          </h2>
<p class="mt-2 text-center text-sm text-subtext-light dark:text-subtext-dark">
            가입 시 입력한 정보로 비밀번호를 재설정할 수 있습니다.
          </p>
</div>
<form action="#" class="mt-8 space-y-6" method="POST">
<div class="rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px">
<div>
<label class="sr-only" for="user-id">ID</label>
<input class="relative block w-full appearance-none rounded-md border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark px-3 py-3 text-text-light dark:text-text-dark placeholder-subtext-light dark:placeholder-subtext-dark focus:z-10 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm" id="user-id" name="id" placeholder="ID 입력" required="" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 pt-4">
<div class="flex-grow">
<label class="sr-only" for="email-address">Email</label>
<input autocomplete="email" class="relative block w-full appearance-none rounded-md border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark px-3 py-3 text-text-light dark:text-text-dark placeholder-subtext-light dark:placeholder-subtext-dark focus:z-10 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm" id="email-address" name="email" placeholder="Email 입력" required="" type="email"/>
</div>
<button class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-primary rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-background-dark transition-colors" type="button">
                인증메일 발송
              </button>
</div>
<div class="pt-4">
<label class="sr-only" for="verification-code">인증코드</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="relative block w-full appearance-none rounded-md border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark px-3 py-3 pr-20 text-text-light dark:text-text-dark placeholder-subtext-light dark:placeholder-subtext-dark focus:z-10 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm" id="verification-code" name="code" placeholder="인증코드 입력" required="" type="text"/>
<span class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center pr-3 text-sm text-subtext-light dark:text-subtext-dark">3:00</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
<button class="text-sm text-primary hover:underline focus:outline-none" type="button">
              재발송
            </button>
</div>
<div>
<button class="group relative flex w-full justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-primary py-3 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-background-dark" type="submit">
              확인
            </button>
</div>
</form>
</div>
</main>
</div>

</body></html>